  ('social-worker-moex-05060', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '青少年的認同類型中，有人從未感受到認同危機，在過渡為成人的過程中也未有任何焦慮或問題， 很早就順從父母意見而決定其自我價值與生涯，這種類型屬於James Marcia分類中的那一種類型？', '["達成認同（identity achievement）", "延期償付（moratorium）", "認同散亂（identity diffusion）", "取消贖回權（foreclosure）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "72531ff92f90", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbf916b39630", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "107", "s": "0605", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05061', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依照皮亞傑（J. Piaget）認知發展階段理論所述，那一個時期的孩童對於倒轉心智的歷程會感到 很困難？', '["運思前期（preoperational stage）", "感覺動作期（sensorimotor stage）", "正式運思期（formal operational stage）", "具體運思期（concrete operational stage）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "72531ff92f90", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbf916b39630", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "107", "s": "0605", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
